  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Xalet Besoli is a cosy, small hotel offering excellent value for money, friendly service and good cuisine, a perfect choice for a relaxed ski holiday.</p>
<h2>Ideal for families</h2>
<p>Hotel Xalet Besoli is ideal if you're wanting a calmer base for your family ski holiday. The hotel is located in a quiet street and the easiest way to get to the ski gondola is on the ski shuttle bus which stops at the end of the road. The hotel also offers a range of facilities for children including cots for bedrooms, free on request and babysitting services. </p>
<h2>Unwind</h2>
<p>Take a moment to relax in the hotel's spacious and modern bar or communal lounge area and share a drink with family and friends. On blue bird days, sit outside on the hotels sun terrace and appreciate the views of the snowy mountains with a hot drink in hand. Before bed, head out onto the balcony, watch the snow fall and cherish that mountainous winter air.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
