  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is approximately 6 minutes' walk (600 metres) to the main ski gondola.</p>
<p>The ski school meeting place and ski hire are located at the top of the gondola.</p>
<p>It is a 4 minute walk (400 metres) to the village centre with all the amenities, bars and nightlife.</p>
<p>The ski shuttle bus stop is just 2 minutes' walk from the hotel.</p>]]></locationDescription>
